      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_35ae806bcc1dfa060d39332b64b430a9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of printed material relating to the history, geography, and politics of the Ivory Coast. Also included are photographs and slides.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
